## 输入/输出
- 输入: BLE 原始字节流（uint8_t* data）+ vehicleTypeCode（如 "DF" 表示 D55/P5）
- 输出: JSON 字符串，drive 节点格式：`{"type":"vehicleState","vehicleState":{"drive":{"shift_state":<gearValue>}}}`

